[[File:Container marking NRSU 421762(4)【 Pictures taken in Japan 】.jpg|thumb|Bureau Veritas marking on a shipping container]]
'''Bureau Veritas S. A.''' (formerly '''BVQI''', '''Bureau Veritas Quality International''') is an international [[certification]] agency. In addition to certifications, they provide HSE expertise (Health, Safety and Environmental). Today the headquarters are in [[Neuilly-sur-Seine]], nearby [[La Défense]]. The company went [[initial public offering|public]] on the [[Paris Bourse]] in October 2007.<ref>{{cite new | url = https://www.ft.com/content/7afbca24-6b9c-11dc-863b-0000779fd2ac | title = Bureau Veritas poised for IPO | first = Adam | last = Jones | location = Paris, France | date = 25 September 2007 | work = Financial Times | publisher = The Financial Times Ltd | access-date = 21 July 2018}}</ref><ref>{{cite news | title = Veritas Goes The Equity Route | first = Lionel | last = Laurent | date = 9 October 2007 | work = Forbes | publisher = Forbes Media LLC }}</ref><ref>{{cite press release | url = http://media.corporate-ir.net/media_files/IROL/21/216209/pr/2007-10-23.pdf | format = PDF | title = Success of Bureau Veritas Initial Public Offering – Offering price set at €37.75 per share | location = Paris, France | date = 23 October  2007 | publisher = Bureau Veritas | access-date = 21 July 2018}}</ref><ref>{{cite new | url = https://www.ft.com/content/51517e00-8201-11dc-8a8f-0000779fd2ac | title = Bureau Veritas poised for IPO | date = 24 October 2007 | work = Financial Times | publisher = The Financial Times Limited | access-date = 21 July 2018}}</ref>

The organization was originally formed in [[Antwerp]] in 1828 as ''Bureau de Renseignements pour les Assurances Maritimes'' (Information Office for Maritime Insurance). The Bureau Veritas name was adopted in 1829.

In 2013, Bureau Veritas bought the company 7layers.<ref>[https://www.elektroniknet.de/markt-technik/messen-testen/bureau-veritas-kauft-7layers-94003.html''Bureau Veritas kauft 7Layers''], [[Markt+Technik]], Nicole Wörner, January 8, 2013. Retrieved on September 29, 2018</ref> Bureau Veritas also launched in this year a video<ref>{{cite web|author=Bureau Veritas WebTV |url=http://en.bureauveritas.tv/386-A_day_with_BV__English_Version.html |title=A day with BV - English Version - Bureau Veritas WebTV - EN |publisher=En.bureauveritas.tv |date= |accessdate=13 August 2014}}</ref> about its main businesses and its Testing, Inspection and Certification activities. This video won the 2014 TopCom "Silver Award" in the External Audiovisual category.<ref>{{cite press release | url = http://topcom.fr/data/TC-Corporate2014/palmaresTCCB14.pdf | dead-url = yes | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20140407092013/http://topcom.fr/data/TC-Corporate2014/palmaresTCCB14.pdf | archive-date = 7 April 2014 | title = TOP/COM GRANDS PRIX | location = Paris, France | date = 6 February 2014 | publisher = TOP/COM Group | access-date = 21 July 2018}}</ref>

