[[Brigadier General]]<ref>[http://www.royalark.net/Persia/pahlavi2.htm Royal Ark]</ref> '''Teymur-Khan Ayromlou''' was a prominent figure in the army of Persia at the start of the twentieth century. [[Tadj ol-Molouk|Queen Tadj ol-Molouk Ayromlou]] was his daughter. The notable [[General Muhammad-Husayn Ayrom]] was his nephew.

